Microwave Green GiantÂ® Cheddar & Bacon Mashed Cauliflower 8 minutes or until softened. Combine Mashed Cauliflower, flour, egg and green onion in medium bowl. Heat 1 tablespoon olive oil in large nonstick skillet over medium heat and cook pancakes (1/4 cup mixture per pancake) 6 minutes or until golden brown, turning once. Repeat with additional oil and batter. Serve pancakes with sour cream, if desired.